{"id":273,"date":"2019-05-06T12:29:19","date_gmt":"2019-05-06T09:29:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/?page_id=273"},"modified":"2024-06-04T15:00:49","modified_gmt":"2024-06-04T12:00:49","slug":"kalite-politikamiz","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/kalite-politikamiz\/","title":{"rendered":"Kalite Politikam\u0131z"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3><\/h3>\n<h3>KAL\u0130TE POL\u0130T\u0130KAMIZ<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Kurumsal de\u011ferlerimiz olan; m\u00fc\u015fterilerimizin kendi pazarlar\u0131nda ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 olmalar\u0131 i\u00e7in \u00e7aba sarf etmeyi ve i\u015f ortaklar\u0131m\u0131zla kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 g\u00fcvene dayal\u0131 \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmay\u0131 , verimli b\u00fcy\u00fcmemizi ve ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 sa\u011flamay\u0131 , m\u00fc\u015fterilerimiz i\u00e7in gelece\u011fe d\u00f6n\u00fck \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmler olu\u015fturarak yenilik\u00e7ilik ilkelerini t\u00fcm \u00e7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131m\u0131zla birlikte benimsemeyi,<\/li>\n<li>Hizmetleri \u00f6nceden belirlenen zaman ve \u015fartlarda, yasal gereklere uygun \u015fekilde eksiksiz olarak sunmay\u0131,<\/li>\n<li>Kalite sistemleri \u00e7er\u00e7evesinde t\u00fcm \u00e7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131n daha yetkin ve yeteneklerini en \u00fcst seviyede kullanabilen ki\u015filer haline gelmeleri i\u00e7in ekip \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131na \u00f6nem vererek kalite d\u00fczeyini s\u00fcrekli y\u00fckseltmeyi,<\/li>\n<li>M\u00fc\u015fteri memnuniyetine her zaman en \u00fcst seviyede de\u011fer verece\u011fimizi,<\/li>\n<li>Tedarik\u00e7ilerimizin ve payda\u015flar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131n s\u00fcrekli geli\u015fimine odakl\u0131 olaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131za,<\/li>\n<li>\u0130\u00e7inde bulundu\u011fumuz topluma ve \u00e7evreye sayg\u0131l\u0131, \u00f6rnek bir kurulu\u015f olmay\u0131 ve i\u015f hacmini s\u00fcrekli geli\u015ftirerek, \u00fclke ekonomisine katk\u0131da bulunmay\u0131,<\/li>\n<li>Yasal kurallara uyaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131,<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7evre ve \u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve i\u015f\u00e7i g\u00fcvenli\u011fi bilincinin yayg\u0131nla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 i\u00e7in \u00fczerimize d\u00fc\u015fen her t\u00fcrl\u00fc konuda g\u00f6revlerimizi, yerine getirece\u011fimizi,<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131n ve faaliyetlerimizden etkilenecek insanlar\u0131n sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131na gelebilecek olumsuz etkileri \u00f6nlemek, kendimizin ve di\u011fer \u015fah\u0131slar\u0131n mal ve m\u00fclkiyetine gelebilecek kaza, hasar ve tehlikeleri daha ba\u015flang\u0131\u00e7 a\u015famas\u0131nda kontrol etmek i\u00e7in gerekli her t\u00fcrl\u00fc korumay\u0131 sa\u011flayaca\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131,<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Taahh\u00fct ediyoruz.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>KAL\u0130TE POL\u0130T\u0130KAMIZ Kurumsal de\u011ferlerimiz olan; m\u00fc\u015fterilerimizin kendi pazarlar\u0131nda ba\u015far\u0131l\u0131 olmalar\u0131 i\u00e7in \u00e7aba sarf etmeyi ve i\u015f ortaklar\u0131m\u0131zla kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131kl\u0131 g\u00fcvene dayal\u0131 \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmay\u0131 , verimli b\u00fcy\u00fcmemizi ve ba\u011f\u0131ms\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z\u0131<span class=\"excerpt-hellip\"> [\u2026]<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-273","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/273"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=273"}],"